|dead-url=no
}}</ref>2006年有教友81,580名，佔轄區總人口百分之1.4。由104名司鐸名管理五十一個堂區。主教一職現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]，榮休主教為{{link-en|加萊拉·普拉薩德|Gallela Prasad}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 10.12.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/10/0920/02000.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715151817/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2018/12/10/0920/02000.html |archivedate=2019-07-15 |language=it |date=2018-12-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

